Massachusetts General Laws chapter 185C,.proposition: This action seeks redress for the Defendant's breach of the covenant of quiet enjoyment, a matter falling within the jurisdiction of the Boston Housing Court pursuant to Massachusetts General Laws chapter 185C, section 3.

Massachusetts General Laws chapter 186,.proposition: The Defendant's repeated failure to provide adequate and consistent heating at the leased premises constitutes a breach of the implied covenant of quiet enjoyment, as codified in Massachusetts General Laws chapter 186, section 14.
